@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_xnxdva(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v1
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.sin((v0 + 0.76 * v1 + 0.65)))
    v2 = wp.exp((tmp - 0.10))
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.32)) / ((v1 + 0.17 + v1 + 0.66) * (v2 + 0.40 * v0 + 0.28)))
    v0 = (((v0 + 0.70 / v2 + 0.81) / 0.18) + wp.cos((tmp + 0.05 / v1 + 0.55)))
    data[tid] = v0
